  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to xdg-dbus-proxy</title>

    <para>
      The <application>xdg-dbus-proxy</application> package contains a filtering
proxy for D-Bus connections. This is useful for forwarding data in and out
of a sandbox.
    </para>

    &lfs120_checked;

